Task
Create an array of n even numbers
Write a function createEvenArray that takes a non-negative integer n as an argument and returns an array containing n even numbers.
Example:
• the createEvenArray (5) function must return [0, 2, 4, 6, 8];
• the createEvenArray (2) function must return [0, 2];
• the createEvenArray (1) function must return [0];
• the createEvenArray (0) function must return [].

Solution
function createEvenArray (n) {
let arr = [];
   for (let i = 0; i <(n * 2); i ++) {
     if (i% 2 === 0) arr.push (i);
   }
     return arr;
}
